                <div class="home-scroll">
                    <a href="#about" class="home-scroll-link"><i class='bx bx-left-arrow-alt' ></i>SCROLL DOWN</a>
                </div>

                <img src="porsche.png" alt="Porsche Sketch" class="home-img">
            </div>
        </section>
    

        <section class="about section" id="about">
            <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>

            <div class="about-container bd-grid">
                <div class="about-img">
                    <img src="garden.png" alt="John Doe image">
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="about-subtitle">I believe with great design, anything is possible.</h2>
                    <span class="about-profession">Digital Design and Development</span>
                    <p class="about-text"></p>

                    <div class="about-social">Hello, I’m Parker Schwendeman, a recent graduate of British Columbia Institute of Technology (BCIT) with a Digital Design and Development Diploma currently in Vancouver.
